column5: Man it,s as tick as peasoup out there.Cants see 3ft in front of ya. Safe driving out there.
I have not got out yet so I don't know how bad it is around here......
It's pretty thick down here too Brian.  Ole Marv and I are just heading out for our morning hike in the woods, sure hope I don't lose the little guy in this soup.
not too bad here in Bradford
Batten down the hatches. There's a monster comin' through.  http://www.intellicast.com/National/Radar/Forecast.aspx
